block %entry [
  $R0 := bvadd(a, b)
  $R1 := bvsub(a, b)
  $R2 := 1
  $R3 := 0
loop_start:
  if $R3 >= 10 goto loop_end
  $R4 := $R0 * $R2
  $R2 := bvadd($R2, 1)
  $R3 := bvadd($R3, 1)
  $R0 := bvxor($R4, $R3)
  goto loop_start
loop_end:
  $R5 := bvadd($R0, b)
  $R6 := $R5 * 7
  $R7 := bvsub($R6, a)
]

block %entry [
    t0 = a + b
    t1 = a - b
    t2 = 1
    t3 = 0

loop_start_0:
    t0 = t0 + t15

    t15 = t15 + 1
    if t15 < 10 goto loop_start_0

    t2 = t0 + t1
    t3 = t0 + t3
    t4 = t1 - t4
    t5 = t2 * t5
    t6 = t3 / t6
    t7 = t4 ^ t7
    t8 = t5 & t8
    t9 = t6 | t9
    t10 = t7 << t10
    t11 = t8 >> t11
    t12 = t9 % t12
    t13 = t10 + t13
    t14 = t11 - t14
    t15 = t12 * t15
    t16 = t13 / t16
    t17 = t14 ^ t17
]
